Before the Right Hon. SIR JOHN VOCE MOORE, KNT., LORD MAYOR of the City of London; the Hon. Sir A. M CHANNELL, Knt., And the Hon. Sir WALTSS PHILLIMORE, Knt., two of the Justices of Her Majesty's High Court; the Right Hon. Sir
CHARLES HALL , K.C.M.G., Q.C., M.P., Recorder of the said City; Sir JOSEPH COCKFIELD DIMSDALE, Knt.; Sir
REGINALD HANSON , Bart., M.P.;
JOHN POUND , Esq.;
WALTER VAUGHAN MORGAN , Esq., and
GEO. WYATT TRUSCOTT , Esq., Aldermen of the said City; Sir FORREST FULTON, Knt., Q.C., Common Serjeant of the said City; Her Majesty's Justices of Oyer and Terminer and General Gaol Delivery, holden for the said City, and Judges of the Central Criminal Court.
